high_descs: Turn around, head through the door and turn left towards the sink.
Take the alarmclock from the sink.
Place the alarmclock in the plate in the sink.
Take the plate with alarm from the sink.
Turn around and go into the bedroom with the alarm towards the desk.
Place the plate with alarm on the desk in the bedroom.
anns.task_desc: Take the Plate with AlarmClock from the toilet and place it on the Desk in the bedroom

high_descs: Exit the room and turn left to reach the sink.
Pick the alarm clock from the wash basin.
Put the alarm clock into the plate kept on the wash basin.
Collect the plate along with the alarm clock.
Turn left to reach the bed room then turn right to reach the desk.
Put the plate along with the alarm clock on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put the Plate along with the AlarmClock on the Desk.

high_descs: Turn around to head out of the room and turn left to head down the passage and reach the sink.
Pick up the alarm clock from the sink.
Put the alarm clock on the plate in the sink.
Pick up the plate from the sink.
Turn around and turn right to head to the desk.
Put the plate on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with the alarm clock on the desk.
